<div class="table">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>1. Income Phase</h3>
            <p>Choose order for each income icon, but fully resolve each</p>
            <ul>
                <li>faction board</li>
                <li>round boosters</li>
                <li>tech tiles</li>
                <li>research board</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>2. Gaia Phase</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Move power: Gaia <span class="arrow"></span> Area I</li>
                <li>Slide a Gaia token under all Gaiaformers that are on transdim planets</li>
                <li>Gaiaformer remains until a mine is built there</li>
                <li>Itars use special ability first, then other players & Terran special ability</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-12">
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h3>3. Action Phase</h3>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Build a mine</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Empty</li>
                <li>Accessible: within navigation range of a colonized planet
                    <ul>
                        <li>boost range with QIC</li>
                        <li>Gaiaformer &ne; colonized</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Habitable
                    <ul>
                        <li>home planet or use terraforming, <i>or</i></li>
                        <li>QIC for Gaia planets <i>or</i></li>
                        <li>mine cost for Gaia planet with Gaiaformer</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Start a Gaia Project</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Move power to Gaia area</li>
                <li>May take from any combination of areas I, II, III</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Upgrade Existing Structures</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><u>Trading Station</u> discount within 2 spaces of an opponent</li>
                <li><u>Planetary Institute</u> gain faction ability</li>
                <li><u>Research Lab</u> gain tech</li>
                <li><u>Academy</u> choose left or right, gain tech</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Form a Federation: </h4>
            <ul>
                <li>7 building power</li>
                <li>Discard 1 power per satellite</li>
                <li>Spaces can hold 1 satellite per player</li>
                <li>Must connect all necessary planets a in single action</li>
                <li>May choose planets further away, but must still take shortest path</li>
                <li>Cannot needlessly include planets with extra satellites</li>
                <li>Gain a federation token, green side up</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">

            <h4>Research Progress</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>4 knowledge</li>
                <li>Max 1 player at level 5 per track</li>
                <li>Advancing to level 5: must flip a federation token from green to gray</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Power and QIC actions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Limt 1<span class="cross"></span> per round</li>
                <li>Spend power or QIC</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Special Actions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Board</li>
                <li>Booster</li>
                <li>Tech</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Pass</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Move turn order cube</li>
                <li>Take <i>any</i> available round booster</li>
                <li>Return current round booster (mandatory, now available for others)</li>
                <li>Apply any red arrow triggers for passing</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Free actions</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Power <span class="arrow"></span> resources</li>
                <li>Discard 1 power from area II to move a token from II to III, may do this even if you have power in area I</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Charge power</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Reaction to a build or upgrade</li>
                <li>Other players may charge power for a building within 2</li>
                <li>1 building max, must choose structure with highest power</li>
                <li>0 / 1 / 2 / 3 vp <span class="arrow"></span> 1 / 2 / 3 / 4 power</li>
                <li>Players who have passed may still charge power</li>
                <li>Edge cases: charge max, vp floor</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-12">
            <hr />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">

            <h3>4. Clean-Up</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Flip boosters face-up</li>
                <li>Reset action tokens</li>
                <li>Remove round scoring tile</li>
            </ul>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>



